ğŸ¬ Generative Extend API
API Specification for AI-Based Video Frame Extension

ğŸ“Œ Purpose

The Generative Extend API allows clients to extend the duration of a video clip by generating new frames using generative AI models.

Use cases:

Smooth transitions

Fix early clip endings

Avoid reshoots

Meet exact video duration requirements

# High level architecture
Client (Editor / App)
