ğŸ§  Core AI Logic (Conceptual)
1. Extract last 0.5â€“1 sec of frames
2. Analyze:
   - Motion vectors
   - Depth
   - Lighting
3. Generate new frames using diffusion / transformer model
4. Validate frame continuity
5. Append frames to original clip
6. Re-encode video

ğŸ“ Constraints & Guardrails

Max extension: 5 seconds

Recommended: 1â€“3 seconds

Disable for dialogue-heavy segments

Reject clips with excessive camera shake

Log all generated frames for audit

